<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>RemindPro - Invoice Reminders for Trades</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <% include partials/nav %>

  <div style="text-align:center;padding:100px 20px;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;">
    <h1 style="font-size:44px;margin-bottom:15px;line-height:1.2;">Never chase a late payment again</h1>
    <p style="font-size:18px;color:#666;margin-bottom:30px;line-height:1.6;">
      RemindPro sends automatic email reminders to your clients when invoices are overdue.
      Stop wasting hours calling and texting — let us handle it.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#888;margin-bottom:30px;">
      One recovered $500 invoice pays for over a year of service.
    </p>
    <a href="/signup" style="display:inline-block;background:#1a1a2e;color:#fff;padding:14px 40px;border-radius:10px;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;">Start Free Trial</a>
    <p style="margin-top:15px;font-size:13px;color:#999;">14-day free trial. No credit card required.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="background:#fff;padding:60px 20px;">
    <div class="container" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));gap:30px;">
      <div style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:36px;font-weight:800;color:#1a1a2e;">1.</div>
        <h3 style="margin:10px 0;">Add Clients & Invoices</h3>
        <p style="color:#666;font-size:14px;">Enter client details and invoice amounts in seconds.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:36px;font-weight:800;color:#1a1a2e;">2.</div>
        <h3 style="margin:10px 0;">Auto-Reminders</h3>
        <p style="color:#666;font-size:14px;">Overdue invoices trigger email reminders every 48 hours.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:36px;font-weight:800;color:#1a1a2e;">3.</div>
        <h3 style="margin:10px 0;">Get Paid Faster</h3>
        <p style="color:#666;font-size:14px;">Clients pay when reminded — no awkward calls needed.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align:center;padding:50px 20px;">
    <p style="color:#999;font-size:13px;">&copy; 2026 RemindPro</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
